    <entry>
      <title>“博客备案过程”</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/12/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/12/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%87%E6%A1%88%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##博客备案<br>因为买的万网域名，需要国内备<br>###网站名称<br>只要是没有违法字符（百度），都可以，但是，真的难想，还要不low，最后起了个“反对幂指三”笑死我了</p><p>###网站备注<br>这个可以上百度抄比如“本网站是个人网站，不含有企业，单位等非个人网站的信息，若在核实中发现网站中含有企业，单位等信息，本人愿与接受以虚假信息进行备案，注销网站，并且主题和域名加入黑名单的处罚。”</p><p>###关闭域名解析<br>在备案前和备案期间，域名不能工作。需要把域名解析暂停掉</p><p>###备案码<br>在“备案狗”买的，10块<br>也可以自己购买服务期，或者直接花100买阿里云的</p><p>###总结<br>备案真难。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Blog调控 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>“终于把live-2d删干净了”</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/11/%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%8Alive-2d%E5%88%A0%E5%B9%B2%E5%87%80%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9D/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/11/%E2%80%9C%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E6%8A%8Alive-2d%E5%88%A0%E5%B9%B2%E5%87%80%E4%BA%86%E2%80%9D/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>##干掉live-2d</p><p>因为这个玩意太烦人了，搞也搞不好，看大佬的成品也不好看，算了，算了</p><p>##如何删除live-2d</p><p>首先删除\themes\next\layout下_layout.swig文件内的与live2d有关的代码</p><p>同时删除所有关于live的设置</p><p>放命令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$npm</span> uninstall hexo-helper-live2d -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再次使用hexo三剑客解决</p><p>用hexo s本地部署查看效果。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Blog调控 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>这是一篇关于hexo的命令文章</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/07/%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Ehexo%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/07/%E8%BF%99%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8Ehexo%E7%9A%84%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="hexo三剑客"><a href="#hexo三剑客" class="headerlink" title="hexo三剑客"></a>hexo三剑客</h2><h3 id="hexo-clean"><a href="#hexo-clean" class="headerlink" title="hexo clean"></a>hexo clean</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>清除缓存文件 db.json 和已生成的静态文件 public。<br>网站显示异常时可以执行这条命令试试。</p><h3 id="hexo-g"><a href="#hexo-g" class="headerlink" title="hexo g"></a>hexo g</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成网站静态文件到默认设置的 public 文件夹。 </p><h3 id="hexo-d"><a href="#hexo-d" class="headerlink" title="hexo d"></a>hexo d</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>自动生成网站静态文件，并部署到设定的仓库。</p><h3 id="hexo-s"><a href="#hexo-s" class="headerlink" title="hexo s"></a>hexo s</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动本地服务器，用于预览主题。</p><p>##话说hexo三剑客居然有四个</p><h3 id="hexo-new-“My-New-Post”"><a href="#hexo-new-“My-New-Post”" class="headerlink" title="hexo new “My New Post”"></a>hexo new “My New Post”</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建立一个新的文章</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> Blog调控 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/2023/03/05/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2023/03/05/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to <a href="https://hexo.io/">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues">GitHub</a>.</p><h2 id="Quick-Start"><a href="#Quick-Start" class="headerlink" title="Quick Start"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
